PrecisApproval to enter into an AGREEMENT RESPECTING ACCESS TO JUSTICE SERVICES with the Government of NUNAVUT which provides for the reimbursement by Canada of some of the costs incurred by Nunavut in providing legal aid in civil or criminal matters, for counselling and referral services, and in public legal education and information.
